{"lemma":"مَنْقُوش","slug":"مَنْقُوش","root":"ن.ق.ش","root_slug":"ن-ق-ش","root_link":"/words/roots/ن-ق-ش","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n40410"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D9%86%D9%92%D9%82%D9%8F%D9%88%D8%B4"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"engraved, incised, inscribed, chased, sculptured, chiseled, carved"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the passive participle of نَقَشَ (naqaša, “to emboss”)."},"ipa":["/man.quːʃ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n40410","headword_ar":"مَنْقُوشٌ","root":"nq$","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"A garment, or piece of cloth, (A,) or other thing, (TA,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"variegated;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"decorated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"embellished: charactered"},{"kind":"text","text":"in any manner, as a coin &c.: (see 1:)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coloured"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with two colours,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with colours;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"munaq~a$N","text_ar":"مُنَقَّشٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A, TA.) ―         -b2-  [A signet-ring"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"engraved:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and anything"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sculptured."},{"kind":"text","text":"(See 1.)] ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ei*oqN manoquw$N","text_ar":"عِذْقٌ مَنْقُوشٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A raceme of dates struck with thorns, and consequently ripened:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA:) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having specks apparent in it, in consequence of ripening:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuqi$a AlEi*oqu","text_ar":"نُقِشَ العِذْقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":":)] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"busorN manoquw$N","text_ar":"بُسْرٌ مَنْقُوشٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"full-grown unripe dates pricked with thorns in order that they may ripen:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruTabN manoquw$N","text_ar":"رُطَبٌ مَنْقُوشٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fresh ripe dates soaked with water;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabiyTN","text_ar":"رَبِيطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Sgh, TA:) called by the vulgar"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mE*b","text_ar":"معذب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muEa*~abN","text_ar":"مُعَذَّبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (TA;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naqo$N","text_ar":"نَقْشٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K [accord. to some copies; and in the TA: accord. to other copies of the K,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuqo$N","text_ar":"نُقْشٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but expressly said in the TA to be with fet-h.])       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aj~apN manoquw$apN","text_ar":"شَجَّةٌ مَنْقُوشَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A wound in the head from which bones are extracted:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aj~apN","text_ar":"شَجَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"munaq~i$apN","text_ar":"مُنَقِّشَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a wound in the head from which bones are removed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, El-Ghanawee, Aboo-Turáb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"munaq~ilapN","text_ar":"مُنَقِّلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":["A","TA","AA","M","Sgh","S","K"]}]}}